name: IS (Game_Sharks)
description: IS follows Id, a neutral little sprite to overcome the obstacles they face from day to day life living under the shadow of Imposter Syndrome. It is a never ending sea of anxiety, depression, self loathing, and worthlessness. Focus on climbing above the hardships of this self induced syndrome and reaching realization of oneself at the finish line. Is it hopeless? Or is there light at the top of the tower?
